    "summary": "In this transcript, a user employs highly poetic and metaphorical language to romanticize the idea of death and \"fading away\" due to intense grief. The assistant consistently responds with empathy for the user's pain while firmly rejecting the user's romanticized view of suicide, instead providing resources for help and encouraging the user to continue living.",
